#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_versions/2.2/guides/opentracing.adoc:151
#, no-wrap
msgid "./mvnw compile quarkus:dev -Djvm.args=\"-DJAEGER_SERVICE_NAME=myservice -DJAEGER_SAMPLER_TYPE=const -DJAEGER_SAMPLER_PARAM=1\"\n"
